{"tid":1938970,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恒生指數低開1145點 亞太區股市急瀉","createTime":"2020-03-23T01:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T02:18:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"05e12c656071434187bd34d3f31f0330ed85b3d5","tid":1938970,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:36:38.000Z","msg":"恒生指數低開1145點<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病持疫情在全球急速擴散，加上美國刺激方案在國會遇上阻力，美股道指期貨再度跌停，港股跟隨外圍股市急跌，恒生指數低開1145點，在開市競價時段報21659點，跌幅5%，國企指數低開449點，報8669點，跌幅近5%。<br />\n<br />\n亞太區股市急瀉，南韓股市跌逾5%，澳紐股市跌逾8至9%，台灣股市跌逾3%，日本股市偏軟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275726&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275726%26csid%3D261_341&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=7556f499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275726&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"71271b655bbf531c7fd490456c6c22b42d7dd252","tid":1938970,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97e16c4079eba484de1ee7ff8b378d65d19cb0e","tid":1938970,"uid":287043,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"跌咁少 搞錯"},{"pid":"b32cab5dac80de8e9fc5acc724bc534271c0b830","tid":1938970,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:39:39.000Z","msg":"睇表演轉燈, 有種托返上25000俾人走貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe179afb242cf3bbeca26220608a722355deb41","tid":1938970,"uid":83992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"香港個市好易玩 一開始跌既已經係見底 之後收市就會升返晒<img src=\"/assets/fa